tion (or the same one), when\nexamples/mini-redis/prompts/implement.md:12:1. Single-threaded event loop using `poll()` for I/O multiplexing\nexamples/mini-redis/prompts/design.md:11:- Single-threaded event loop using `poll()` (not `select()`, not `epoll()`)","numLines":32}}
